title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 §§ 151-1.2 - Specific approval

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 §§ 151-1.2 - Specific approval

State Regulations

No workers' compensation rate filing shall be made effective by any rate service organization or insurer until an appropriate workers' compensation rate has been specifically approved by the superintendent. Notes
